                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6969" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1082</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8802 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">金融中介的利益冲突——以康美药业为例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Conflicts of Interest of Financial Intermediaries —— A Case Study of Kangmei Pharmaceutical Co.,Ltd</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">伍燕然，郑舒婷，孙寅辉</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">康美药业股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">利益冲突；金融中介；独立董事；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Conflict of interest;Financial intermediaries;Independent directors</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">近年来，随着上市公司数量与日俱增，上市公司的财务造假事件也层出不穷，其影响之恶劣已超出经济领域，逐渐演变成为社会各界都十分关心的话题。前段时间，康美药业299亿元货币资金财务造假案就引发了社会各界的高度关注，曾经备受分析师追捧的康美药业，因财务造假而最终沦为股市“黑天鹅”。作为康美药业承销保荐机构的广发证券、审计机构的正中珠江会计师事务所乃至独立董事难辞其咎，接连被罚。本案例以康美药业为研究对象，描述了康美药业从一只医药企业的“白马股”到因财务造假而最终沦为股市“黑天鹅”的过程，探讨研究分析师、投资银行、会计师事务所等金融中介和独立董事与康美药业在这过程中隐藏的利益冲突，呈现了利益冲突所产生的后果，以及寻找减少利益冲突的方法。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In recent years, with the increasing number of listed companies, the financial fraud incidents of listed companies have emerged in an endless stream, and their bad influence has gone beyond the economic field and gradually evolved into a topic of great concern to all sectors of society.  Some time ago, Kangmei Pharmaceutical&#39;s financial fraud has aroused great concern of the regulatory authorities and investors.  Kangmei Pharmaceutical, which was highly recommended by analysts for a long time, eventually became a &quot;black swan&quot; in the stock market due to financial fraud. Affected by Kangmei Pharmaceutical, GF Securities, Zhengzhong Zhujiang Accounting Firms and independent directors were punished one after another.  Taking Kangmei Pharmaceutical as the research object, this case describes the process of Kangmei Pharmaceutical from a &quot;white horse stock&quot; to a &quot;black swan&quot; in the stock market due to the financial fraud, and discusses the conflicts of interest between financial intermediaries such as analysts, investment banks and accounting firms and independent directors and Kangmei Pharmaceutical in this process,  presents the consequences of the conflicts of interest, and seeks ways to reduce the conflict of interest. </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《金融学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">信息不对称；利益冲突；委托代理理论；金融中介的界定；乐观偏差；分析师利益冲突；利益冲突；委托代理理论；审计冲突；利益冲突；委托代理理论；灰色董事；利益冲突缓解办法</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
